"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-14-imane-khelif-names-jk-rowling-elon-musk-cyberbullying-lawsuit-olympics-win-21418069\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Elon Muskand J.K. Rowling have been named ina lawsuit filed to French authoritiesover alleged 'cyber harassment' againstOlympicchampion boxerImane Khelif.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 154, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13, \"end\": 17, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.611451204204185e-22, \"text\": \"J.K.\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\"}, {\"begin\": 63, \"end\": 69, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9915054257372334, \"rank\": 0.008517674863399513, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nabil Boudi, Khelif's attorney, has confirmed that the criminal complaint has been filed with theParispublic prosecutor's office last Friday.\", \"from\": 156, \"to\": 297, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'J.\", \"from\": 299, \"to\": 302, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"K. Rowling and Elon Musk are named in the lawsuit, among others,' Boudi toldVariety.\", \"from\": 303, \"to\": 387, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 303, \"end\": 305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Kirkpatrick\", \"score\": 0.9969718443707978, \"rank\": 0.0030266384571986616, \"text\": \"K.\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Kirkpatrick\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Kirkpatrick\"}, {\"begin\": 318, \"end\": 327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Elon Musk\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'[Donald] Trump tweeted, so whether or not he is named in our lawsuit, he will inevitably be looked into as part of the prosecution.\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 521, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'What we are asking is that the prosecution investigates not only these people but whoever it feels necessary.\", \"from\": 523, \"to\": 633, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If the case goes to court, they will stand trial.'\", \"from\": 634, \"to\": 684, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The lawsuit has been filed against X, the social media platform owned by Musk, which means that under French law it was filed against unknown persons.\", \"from\": 686, \"to\": 836, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 788, \"end\": 798, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_of_France\", \"score\": 0.9995264853696724, \"rank\": 0.0004096132611134869, \"text\": \"French law\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_of_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The lawsuit accuses X of facilitating 'acts of aggravated cyber harassment'.\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 913, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's the responsibility of lawmakers to issue sanctions to platforms, not ours,' Boudi said.\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 1008, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif, who became Algeria's first Olympic gold medallist in women's boxing and their first boxer to win gold since 1996, faced scrutiny over her participation in Paris after she was disqualified from the Women's World Championships last year for failing the International Boxing Association's (IBA)gendereligibility rules.\", \"from\": 1010, \"to\": 1333, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1029, \"end\": 1036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.999999957197816, \"rank\": 2.628906415717682e-08, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 1173, \"end\": 1178, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999998468511084, \"rank\": 1.531491169446901e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1269, \"end\": 1301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8125253491874872e-20, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 25-year-old has always competed in the women's boxing divisionand has identified as female since birth.\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1442, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Harry Potter author Rowling was among the high-profile voices who spoke out against Khelif's participation against other female boxers.\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1579, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1444, \"end\": 1456, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Potter\", \"score\": 0.9999999032616007, \"rank\": 7.857284218113857e-08, \"text\": \"Harry Potter\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Potter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Potter\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After Khelif's win over Angela Carini, Rowling posted an image on X of the Italian in tears after she chose to withdraw from her fight against the Algerian and wrote: 'Could any picture sum up our new men's rights movement better?\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1811, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1605, \"end\": 1618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103660394, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 1728, \"end\": 1736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.99442990769281, \"rank\": 0.005600442074374098, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The smirk of a male who's knows he's protected by a misogynist sporting establishment enjoying the distress of a woman he's just punched in the head, and whose life's ambition he's just shattered.'\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 2011, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Musk, meanwhile, shared a post from American swimmer Riley Gaines which read: 'Men do not belong in women's sports'.\", \"from\": 2013, \"to\": 2129, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2049, \"end\": 2057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999985621899545, \"rank\": 1.433204856840376e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2066, \"end\": 2071, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riley_Finn\", \"score\": 0.9999999165006591, \"rank\": 7.426860608158231e-08, \"text\": \"Riley\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riley_Finn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riley_Finn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Musk added to the message by writing: 'Absolutely.'\", \"from\": 2130, \"to\": 2181, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On his Truth Social outlet, Trump wrote: 'I will keep men out of women's sports.'\", \"from\": 2183, \"to\": 2264, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2211, \"end\": 2216, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999955851210102, \"rank\": 4.414891498578912e-06, \"text\": \"Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking after her gold medal win in Paris, Khelif described those who have raised doubts over her gender as 'the enemies of success'.\", \"from\": 2266, \"to\": 2400, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2303, \"end\": 2308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999998468511084, \"rank\": 1.531491169446901e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Now the whole world knows the story of Imane Khelif,' she said.\", \"from\": 2402, \"to\": 2466, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2442, \"end\": 2454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's a dream for every athlete.\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2500, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If I qualify or not?\", \"from\": 2501, \"to\": 2521, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If I am a woman or not?\", \"from\": 2522, \"to\": 2545, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I made many statements in the media.\", \"from\": 2546, \"to\": 2582, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am fully qualified, I am a woman, I was born a woman, I lived a woman, there is no doubt about that.\", \"from\": 2583, \"to\": 2685, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'These people [who claim I am not], they are the enemies of success, it's what I call them, it gives my success a special taste because of these attacks.\", \"from\": 2687, \"to\": 2840, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I hope that people will commit to the Olympic charter and its values.\", \"from\": 2842, \"to\": 2912, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are here to perform to our audience and families.\", \"from\": 2913, \"to\": 2965, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I hope we will not see similar attacks in these Olympics.'\", \"from\": 2966, \"to\": 3024, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 3026, \"to\": 3074, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 3076, \"to\": 3146, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Team GB star completed Olympics marathon with broken leg: 'Downhills were hell!'\", \"from\": 3148, \"to\": 3238, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Team GB star Adam Peaty makes retirement decision after Paris Olympics  ArrowMORE:How to delete your X account after app becomes toxic 'place of misery'  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 3240, \"to\": 3514, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3263, \"end\": 3273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}, {\"begin\": 3306, \"end\": 3320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know which team you support.Close  This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 3516, \"to\": 3647, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Y